#: ui/MainWindow.glade:1013
msgid "Submit"
msgstr "Bidali"

#: ui/MainWindow.glade:1039
msgid ""
"The information shared will only be used for hardware compatibility "
"statistics and to be able to troubleshoot compatibility issues in advance.\n"
"\n"
"No personal data is collected.\n"
"\n"
"Hardware information is not shared with third parties and is only sent once "
"during this process."
msgstr ""
"Partekatutako informazioa hardwarearen bateragarritasun-estatistiketarako "
"eta bateragarritasun-arazoak aldez aurretik konpontzeko soilik erabiliko "
"da.\n"
"\n"
"Ez da datu pertsonalik biltzen.\n"
"\n"
"Hardwareari buruzko informazioa ez da hirugarrenekin partekatzen eta prozesu "
"honetan behin bakarrik bidaltzen da."

#: ui/MainWindow.glade:1068
msgid "Below is the data which will be sent:"
msgstr "Jarraian bidaliko diren datuak daude:"

